@HostAddress = http://localhost:5163
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ================= AUTH ENDPOINTS =================

### 1. Register User (Candidate)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Test Candidate",
  "email": "candidate@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "Candidate"
}

### 2. Login User (Get JWT Token)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "candidate@test.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### ================= JOB ENDPOINTS =================

### 3. Get All Active Jobs
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 4. Create Job (Recruiter / Admin)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/jobs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Full-Stack Software Engineer",
  "description": "Looking for C# ASP.NET Core and React developer.",
  "requiredSkills": "C#, ASP.NET Core, React, SQL Server",
  "jobRole": "Software Engineer",
  "employmentType": "FullTime",
  "location": "Remote",
  "organizationId": 1,
  "departmentId": 1,
  "closingDate": "2026-12-31T23:59:59"
}

### ================= APPLICATION ENDPOINTS =================

### 5. Apply for a Job (Candidate)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/applications/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "jobId": 1,
  "candidateCVId": "1"
}

### 6. Get Staff Applications (Recruiter / Hiring Manager)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/applications
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 7. Shortlist Application (Recruiter)
PUT {{HostAddress}}/api/applications/1/shortlist
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 8. Reject Application (Recruiter)
PUT {{HostAddress}}/api/applications/1/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Make Final Hiring Decision (Hiring Manager)
PUT {{HostAddress}}/api/applications/1/decision?decision=Selected
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ================= INTERVIEW ENDPOINTS =================

### 10. Schedule Interview (Recruiter)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/interviews
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "applicationId": 1,
  "interviewerId": 2,
  "interviewDate": "2026-08-01T10:00:00",
  "interviewMode": "Online",
  "meetingLink": "https://meet.google.com/abc-defg-hij"
}

### 11. Get My Interview Calendar
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/interviews/my-calendar
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 12. Enhance Feedback with AI (Hiring Manager / Recruiter)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/interviews/enhance-feedback
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rawNotes": "good technical interview strong c# and react knowledge",
  "candidateName": "Test Candidate",
  "jobTitle": "Full-Stack Software Engineer"
}

### ================= ADMIN ENDPOINTS =================

### 13. Get Admin Dashboard Metrics
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 14. Get All Users (Admin)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 15. Get System Audit Logs (Admin)
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/admin/auditlogs
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
